name: Null And Void (FatiguedFox, Minty)
description:
-Submission To Mini Jam 67-

- Theme: Void - Limitation: No Enemies -

After recently gaining the ability to temporarily delete certain physical objects, a young bunny is driven to insanity until they finally delete themselves...

However,  they find themselves in the Void, an empty space with nothing but random blocks scattered around. Unable to bring them self back, they explore the vast and infinite abyss.

Use your new found ability to collect the Void Stones, to hopefully bring them back home.

----------------------------------------------

Controls:

WASD  /  Arrow Keys - To Move

W  /  Up Arrow Key - Jump

Left Mouse Click - To Interact
